com.yworks.yfiles.view

Class GraphOverviewControl

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.Parent
        • javafx.scene.layout.Region
          • javafx.scene.control.Control
            • com.yworks.yfiles.view.CanvasControl
              • com.yworks.yfiles.view.GraphOverviewControl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ILookup, javafx.css.Styleable, EventTarget, Skinnable

    public class GraphOverviewControl
extends CanvasControl
    Convenience control implementation that shows an overview of an IGraph contained in another GraphControl.

    This control uses a GraphVisualCreator to display the graph in a preview mode and an OverviewInputMode to allow for easily navigating in the GraphControl.

    The GraphOverviewControl may be styled with backgrounds and borders using CSS. It has all styleproperties of StackPane.
